Date: 15 Mar 2001
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>

We hear from a reliable source that, as of the end of February 2001, there
have been cases of suspected Lassa fever in Edo State, southern Nigeria.
ProMED-mail would be interested in receiving further details.
